Computers do not know human languages like English or Turkish
These machines can only speak in 0 and 1's
All electronics communicate by binalry language which is only consist of 0's and 1's
Progamming languages are the bridges between Humans and Computers
Interpreters and Compilers are the programs that translate written code to machine language so that the computer will compile what we write
Interpreters go line by line on our code to translate what we have written into machine/computer language
Compilers take the whole code at once and turn it into machine language at once.
